1. *Lika* je prelepo planinsko područje u Hrvatskoj. (Lika is a beautiful mountainous region in Croatia.)
2. Posetili smo *liku* našeg pokojnog dede prošlog vikenda. (We visited the likeness of our late grandfather last weekend.)
3. Kada je video svog prijatelja, počeo je da se smeje i rekao: "E, pa *lika* si mi ti!" (When he saw his friend, he started laughing and said: "Hey, you're my man!")
4. *Like* namirnice mogu biti jako ukusne i zdrave. (Vegetable-based foods can be very tasty and healthy.)
5. Rekao je da je *lična* karta jedini dokument koji mu je potreban. (He said that his ID card is the only document he needs.)
6. Da li si video *liku* koja je prošla pored nas pre nekoliko minuta? (Did you see the guy who passed us a few minutes ago?)
7. Sve *like* koji su bili prisutni su bili izuzetno zadovoljni. (All the people who were present were extremely satisfied.)
8. Uzmi ovaj *lični* predmet sa sobom kada budeš odlazio. (Take this personal item with you when you leave.)
9. Neki ljudi kažu da *like* nemaju dovoljno karaktera da se bave teškim poslovima. (Some people say that men lack the character to deal with difficult jobs.)
10. Ukoliko ne poznajete *liku* koju želite da sretnete, možete se raspitati kod drugih ljudi. (If you don't know the person you want to meet, you can ask other people for information about them.)